androidx.lifecycle

Interface ViewModelStoreOwner

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AmbientModeSupport, AppCompatActivity, AppCompatDialogFragment, BaseSupportFragment, BrandedSupportFragment, BrowseSupportFragment, CarDrawerActivity, DetailsSupportFragment, DialogFragment, EditTextPreferenceDialogFragmentCompat, ErrorSupportFragment, Fragment, FragmentActivity, GuidedStepSupportFragment, GuidedStepSupportFragment.DummyFragment, HeadersSupportFragment, ListFragment, ListPreferenceDialogFragmentCompat, MediaRouteChooserDialogFragment, MediaRouteControllerDialogFragment, MediaRouteDiscoveryFragment, MultiSelectListPreferenceDialogFragmentCompat, OnboardingSupportFragment, PlaybackSupportFragment, PreferenceDialogFragmentCompat, PreferenceFragmentCompat, RowsSupportFragment, SearchSupportFragment, VerticalGridSupportFragment, VideoSupportFragment

    public interface ViewModelStoreOwner
    A scope that owns ViewModelStore.

    A responsibility of an implementation of this interface is to retain owned ViewModelStore during the configuration changes and call ViewModelStore.clear(), when this scope is going to be destroyed.
